        <canEscalate>false</canEscalate>
        <description>This agent invokes when user wants to log an expense record into the system. The expense amount, vendor, receipt #, transaction date, visit and expense type are all to be linked. The expense might contain line items as well for which amount and name are to be noted and linked to the parent expense.</description>
        <developerName>Expense_Automation_16jak000001nn8f</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>The value for expense type must be set by you based on what user has conversed, set it to any of these following values: use the last value if none of the other values match:
You must use Business Meals whenever for dinner, breakfast, brunch, lunch, you must decide
Business Meals, Conference Registration, Educational Grants, Educational Materials, Lodging,, Mileage / Fuel, Parking &amp; Tolls, Product Samples, Promotional Items / Gifts, Public Transport, Speaker Fees / Honoraria, Sponsorships, Doctor Meeting Expenses</description>
