        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If user provides Visit Name, Use Query record to query the Visit__c to get the record Id. Visit Name format would be: &quot;Visit-{xxxxxxx}&quot; Using Query Records, query the record Id and map it to: varVisitId</description>
            <developerName>instructions_3_1777735938922</developerName>
